OL,6,FA teenager who carried out a glass
OL,7,Fattack on a 12-year-old girl and two
OL,8,Fmembers of staff at his former school
OL,9,Fafter warning "today is the day" has
OL,10,Fbeen convicted of three counts of
OL,11,Fattempting to cause grievous bodily
OL,12,Fharm.
OL,14,FLouis Melotte, 17, can be named for
OL,15,Fthe first time as the boy responsible
OL,16,Fafter a judge at Sheffield Crown Court
OL,17,Flifted an order protecting his
OL,18,Fidentity.
