OL,6,FHis trial heard he posted a series of
OL,7,Fchilling messages on social media
OL,8,Fbefore the incident at Birley Academy
OL,9,Fin Sheffield on 1 May.
OL,11,FHe wrote "today is the day", warned a
OL,12,Fstaff member not to attend work and
OL,13,Freferred to a second staff member as
OL,14,Fan "absolute traitor", saying, "I
OL,15,Fhaven't forgotten you either."
OL,17,FMelotte walked into the school and
OL,18,Fasked for a staff member who had not
OL,19,Farrived, when the schoolgirl and two
OL,20,Ffriends entered the area.
