OL,6,FThe court heard he attacked the girl
OL,7,Fwithout warning with a piece of broken
OL,8,Fglass.
OL,10,FA youth mentor who was in the area
OL,11,Ftried to intervene and was also
OL,12,Fattacked, while a receptionist ushered
OL,13,Fthe three girls away.
OL,15,FThe youth mentor then tried to
OL,16,Frestrain the boy and recalled him
OL,17,Fsaying: "This was meant to happen".
OL,19,FProsecutor, Katy Rafter, said the boy
OL,20,Fgot away and tried to attack the
OL,21,Freceptionist.
