OL,6,FBoth the youth worker and receptionist
OL,7,Fwere scratched during the incident,
OL,8,Fwhich forced the school to go into
OL,9,Flockdown.
OL,11,FMs Rafter told the court about a
OL,12,FSnapchat conversation, in which
OL,13,FMelotte warned another user to stay
OL,14,Faway from the school on the day in
OL,15,Fquestion.
OL,17,FHe said that the school was "done for"
OL,18,Fand that he would be "arrested
OL,19,Fafterwards, in jail or dead."
