OL,6,FWhen he was arrested, Melotte made
OL,7,Fcomments about "accepting Jesus Christ
OL,8,Fas your Lord and saviour".
OL,10,FHe admitted possessing a sharply
OL,11,Fpointed article and two counts of
OL,12,Fwounding without intent but pleaded
OL,13,Fnot guilty to three counts of
OL,14,Fattempting cause grievous bodily harm.
OL,16,FHowever, he was found guilty of three
OL,17,Fcounts of attempting to cause grievous
OL,18,Fbodily harm with intent on Wednesday.
