OL,6,FDetective Constable Thomas Ryan
OL,7,Fcommended staff at Birley Academy for
OL,8,Ftheir bravery.
OL,10,FHe said, "Their courage undoubtedly
OL,11,Freduced the level of injuries
OL,12,Fsustained and the number of victims,
OL,13,Fand the school has continued to
OL,14,Fcooperate with us over the course of
OL,15,Fthis investigation."
OL,17,FMelotte has been remanded in custody
OL,18,Fand will be sentenced on 23 August at
OL,19,FSheffield Crown Court.
